videos.headline: Tate keeps option himself for long TD run
videos.description: Arizona QB Khalil Tate keeps the read-option and sprints 58 yards into the end zone for the game's first score.

videos.headline: Colorado caps 10-play drive with rushing TD
videos.description: Colorado's Phillip Lindsay runs it in from five yards out to tie Arizona 7-7 in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Tate gets loose for second score
videos.description: Arizona QB Khalil Tate sprints to the left on a designed run and outruns the Colorado defense to the end zone for a 28-yard score.

videos.headline: Lindsay scores on 19th play of drive
videos.description: Colorado's Phillip Lindsay scores for the second time on a one-yard run capping a 19-play drive and tying the game 14-14.

videos.headline: Tate beats Colorado with his arm
videos.description: After rushing for two long scores, Arizona QB Khalil Tate finds a wide open Shun Brown for a 13-yard TD throw and catch.

videos.headline: Tate runs for third 25-plus yard TD
videos.description: After a third rushing touchdown for 47 yards, Arizona QB Khalil Tate has six carries for 172 yards and three scores.

videos.headline: Bobo beats defender inside for TD catch
videos.description: Colorado QB Steven Montez finishes another long, 15-play drive with a seven-yard touchdown pass to Bryce Bobo.

videos.headline: Arizona QB hurt on late hit
videos.description: Arizona starting QB Brandon Dawkins has to leave the game following a late hit in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Offensive line does the work on TD run
videos.description: Arizona RB Zach Green follows his blockers for an easy one-yard TD run to go up 35-21.

videos.headline: Montez throws pop-pass for TD
videos.description: Colorado QB Steven Montez fakes the QB draw, jumps and throws to Chris Bounds for the two-yard TD as Colorado trails Arizona 35-28.

videos.headline: QB Tate outruns entire defense for fourth TD
videos.description: Arizona's QB Khalil Tate rushes for his fourth TD of the day with a 75-yard scramble to give him 290 rushing yards.

videos.headline: Play-action frees Bounds for second TD
videos.description: Colorado's QB Steven Montez fools the Arizona defense with a play-action fake and finds a wide open Chris Bounds for a 39-yard score as Colorado trails 42-35.

videos.headline: Tate-Ellison connections sets up FG
videos.description: Arizona QB Khalil Tate finds Tony Ellison streaking downfield for 60 yards on a post route to set up a field goal.

videos.headline: Lindsay keeps Colorado in it with TD
videos.description: Colorado RB Phillip Lindsay scores from 11 yards out to give him 281 yards and two scores on 41 carries.
